    {
     "text": "Default value (=Flat Profile) is set to $FFE5 = -27(DEC signed) = -3.375 dB Example if value read/write is $FFE3 = -29 (DEC signed) ==> Formula:-29 = -27+X*/0.125 X* = -0.25 *X (dB) = Increase or Decrease of AFE Gain Calibration compare to Default value (-3.375 dB) ==> AFE Gain Calibration = -3.375 (Default value)+X AFE Gain Calibration = -3.375 (Default value) + (-0.25) = -3.625 dB",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
